    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The \"value\" being provided is being weighed against the environmental cost of the compute you use. The decision has pretty much been made at the executive level; the priority is meeting the sustainability targets. The L-Series handles the majority of the volume, which is what we need for our numbers. It's just the direction the company is going in now.",
